703103f-a.text: Bath Ave., east side, between Bay 22nd and 23rd. The two frame buildings at the corners, from left to right, are Nos. [Numbers] 1945-1949 Bath Ave. To the right of the brick building at the extreme left, is a frame house that does not appear in the 1929 Brooklyn Atlas. [Date] March 1925.
